ooth, eye-catching motion within a fast-paced environment.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Execution</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Leveraging bold typography and kinetic movements, the animation embraces a rhythmic and energetic visual language. The structure keeps the viewer focused on key messages while maintaining an engaging loop suited for social media.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"next-project-nav mt-4\">\n    <div class=\"container text-center\">\n      <p class=\"label\">[CONTINUE]</p>\n      <a href=\"project-samsung.html\" class=\"mega-title hover-accent\">Next Project <svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7\"/></svg></a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</main>\n\n<footer class=\"site-footer\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"footer-grid\">\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">MULTIMEDIA DESIGNER</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Embracing imperfection.<br>Finding beauty in the raw.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">NAVIGATION</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"index.html\">Home</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"work.html\">Work</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"about.html\">About</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">CONNECT</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/amielnavigar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LinkedIn</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer-bottom\">\n      <div class=\"copyright\">© 2026</div>\n      <div class=\"quote\">Nothing is permanent.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>