de-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container split-layout\">\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Challenge</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Stripping away the excess to reveal the core message within a crowded digital landscape. The objective was to prioritize raw function over decorative polish to capture attention quickly and cleanly on social feeds.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Execution</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Utilizing stark contrasts and unyielding grids to frame the asset. Imperfections in texture are embraced, allowing the inherent visual qualities of the media to speak for themselves, unfiltered and honest.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"next-project-nav mt-4\">\n    <div class=\"container text-center\">\n      <p class=\"label\">[CONTINUE]</p>\n      <a href=\"work.html\" class=\"mega-title hover-accent\">Next Project <svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7\"/></svg></a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</main>\n\n<footer class=\"site-footer\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"footer-grid\">\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">MULTIMEDIA DESIGNER</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Embracing imperfection.<br>Finding beauty in the raw.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">NAVIGATION</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"index.html\">Home</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"work.html\">Work</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"about.html\">About</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">CONNECT</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"https: