uthenticity, and technical precision. Visually, the design adopts a \"white minimal\" aesthetic, utilizing a clean white backdrop, elegant navy blue accents, and traditional, detailed botanical illustrations to communicate premium quality and a deep respect for coffee tradition.\n\nDesign Elements:\n\n\n\nThe Blueprint Botanical: The central visual element is a detailed, traditional pen-and-ink style illustration of the coffee plant, rendered in a calming navy blue. This \"blueprint\" style suggests meticulous study, expertise, and an authentic, organic origin. It connects the consumer directly to the farm.\n\nThe Contrast Header: A solid navy blue block at the bottom provides a strong structural base. It utilizes bold, clean white typography for essential product details ensuring maximum readability against the minimal top section. A subtle geometric pattern adds texture without distraction.\n\n\n\n\n\nPurpose:\n\nThe primary purpose of the white minimal design is to convey unparalleled sophistication and purity. By stripping away excessive color and complex imagery, the label signals that the coffee itself is the star, requiring no gimmicks. The minimal design addresses a discerning consumer who values transparency and authenticity.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2024 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/4gw2lx789-2024 Coffee Design - Main 3.png","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/dc6de7db-7ec8-4447-9a54-18a3f9770c29"},{"id":"jgp27redn","name":"2024 Coffee Design - CHERRY CABANDAY.jpg","url":"asset://jgp27redn","type":"image","year":"2024","description":"This label design is a sophisticated product sticker intended for a curated coffee pouch, focusing on craftsmanship, authenticity, and technical precision. Visually, the design adopts a \"white minimal\" aesthetic, utilizing a clean white backdrop, elegant navy blue accents, and traditional, detailed botanical illustrations to communicate premium quality and a deep respect for coffee tradition.\n\nDesign Elements:\n\n\n\nThe Blueprint Botanical: The central visual element is a detailed, traditional pen-and-ink style illustration of the coffee plant, rendered in a calming navy blue. This \"blueprint\" style suggests meticulous study, expertise, and an authentic, organic origin. It connects the consumer directly to the farm.\n\nThe Contrast Header: A solid navy blue block at the bottom provides a strong structural base. It utilizes bold, clean white typography for essential product details ensuring maximum readability against the minimal top section. A subtle geometric pattern adds texture without distraction.\n\n\n\n\n\nPurpose:\n\nThe primary purpose of the white minimal design is to convey unparalleled sophistication and purity. By stripping away excessive color and complex imagery, the label signals that the coffee itself is the star, requiring no gimmicks. The minimal design addresses a discerning consumer who values transparency and authenticity.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2024 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/jgp27redn-2024 Coffee Design - CHERRY CABANDAY.jpg","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/9247c616-08e9-4063-9f80-d5a9a0918929"},{"id":"qsaxa86pb","name":"2024 Coffee Design - Milalittra Natural.png","url":"asset://qsaxa86pb","type":"image","year":"2024","description":"This label design is a sophisticated product sticker intended for a curated coffee pouch, focusing on craftsmanship, authenticity, and technical precision. Visually, the design adopts a \"white minimal\" aesthetic, utilizing a clean white backdrop, elegant navy blue accents, and traditional, detailed botanical illustrations to communicate premium quality and a deep respect for coffee tradition.\n\nDesign Elements:\n\n\n\nThe Blueprint Botanical: The central visual element is a detailed, traditional pen-and-ink style illustration of the coffee plant, rendered in a calming navy blue. This \"blueprint\" style suggests meticulous study, expertise, and an authentic, organic origin. It connects the consumer directly to the farm.\n\nThe Contrast Header: A solid navy blue block at the bottom provides a strong structural base. It utilizes bold, clean white typography for essential product details ensuring maximum readability against the minimal top section. A subtle geometric pattern adds texture without distraction.\n\n\n\n\n\nPurpose:\n\nThe primary purpose of the white minimal design is to convey unparalleled sophistication and purity. By stripping away excessive color and complex imagery, the label signals that the coffee itself is the star, requiring no gimmicks. The minimal design addresses a discerning consumer who values transparency and authenticity.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2024 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/qsaxa86pb-2024 Coffee Design - Milalittra Natural.png","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/d10ab973-b5e0-4d66-8cbc-63de3c8d4a19"},{"id":"ptoe8lsln","name":"2024 Coffee Design - Marivic Dubria.jpg","url":"asset://ptoe8lsln","type":"image","year":"2024","description":"This label design is a sophisticated product sticker intended for a curated coffee pouch, focusing on craftsmanship, authenticity, and technical precision. Visually, the design adopts a \"white minimal\" aesthetic, utilizing a clean white backdrop, elegant navy blue accents, and traditional, detailed botanical illustrations to communicate premium quality and a deep respect for coffee tradition.\n\nDesign Elements:\n\n\n\nThe Blueprint Botanical: The central visual element is a detailed, traditional pen-and-ink style illustration of the coffee plant, rendered in a calming navy blue. This \"blueprint\" style suggests meticulous study, expertise, and an authentic, organic origin. It connects the consumer directly to the farm.\n\nThe Contrast Header: A solid navy blue block at the bottom provides a strong structural base. It utilizes bold, clean white typography for essential product details ensuring maximum readability against the minimal top section. A subtle geometric pattern adds texture without distraction.\n\n\n\n\n\nPurpose:\n\nThe primary purpose of the white minimal design is to convey unparalleled sophistication and purity. By stripping away excessive color and complex imagery, the label signals that the coffee itself is the star, requiring no gimmicks. The minimal design addresses a discerning consumer who values transparency and authenticity.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2024 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/ptoe8lsln-2024 Coffee Design - Marivic Dubria.jpg","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/a448ba70-f40d-4a76-ab05-71452a8f88f6"},{"id":"cbvmw6hfp","name":"2025 Coffee Design - Main2.png","url":"asset://cbvmw6hfp","type":"image","year":"2025","description":"Design Elements:\n\nThe Red: Bold, detailed clusters of ripe coffee cherries dominate the lower half, symbolizing peak flavor and readiness for harvest. This is reinforced by a vertical red divider bar.\n\nThe Yellow: A warm, inviting backdrop of a patterned yellow hue suggests the tropical sun and a bright, sunny acidity. Subtly outlined botanical elements add texture without clutter.\n\nThe Green: Distinctive green coffee leaves frame the cherry clusters, representing the natural, organic origin and fresh growth.\n\n\n\nPurpose:\nThe primary purpose of the design is to establish the coffee's exclusive and artisanal nature. The very small net weight of only 50g instantly signals a rare micro-lot or a special sampler pack. The specific, complex tasting notes are not merely described but presented as essential components, guiding the consumer through the curated flavor profile. The design transforms the label from a simple identification marker into a narrative of quality, care, and origin, elevating the coffee from a commodity to an exclusive experience.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2025 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/cbvmw6hfp-2025 Coffee Design - Main2.png","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/264577b1-4a8d-45a4-b958-7e00a377f937"},{"id":"rztlfjgg7","name":"2025 Coffee Design - Reyjohn Basco.jpg","url":"asset://rztlfjgg7","type":"image","year":"2025","description":"Design Elements:\n\nThe Red: Bold, detailed clusters of ripe coffee cherries dominate the lower half, symbolizing peak flavor and readiness for harvest. This is reinforced by a vertical red divider bar.\n\nThe Yellow: A warm, inviting backdrop of a patterned yellow hue suggests the tropical sun and a bright, sunny acidity. Subtly outlined botanical elements add texture without clutter.\n\nThe Green: Distinctive green coffee leaves frame the cherry clusters, representing the natural, organic origin and fresh growth.\n\n\n\nPurpose:\nThe primary purpose of the design is to establish the coffee's exclusive and artisanal nature. The very small net weight of only 50g instantly signals a rare micro-lot or a special sampler pack. The specific, complex tasting notes are not merely described but presented as essential components, guiding the consumer through the curated flavor profile. The design transforms the label from a simple identification marker into a narrative of quality, care, and origin, elevating the coffee from a commodity to an exclusive experience.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2025 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/rztlfjgg7-2025 Coffee Design - Reyjohn Basco.jpg","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/2487aa85-0555-4455-9ffb-7dbc541ae2ba"},{"id":"k12bvi1ml","name":"2025 Coffee Design - Unleashed.jpg","url":"asset://k12bvi1ml","type":"image","year":"2025","description":"Design Elements:\n\nThe Red: Bold, detailed clusters of ripe coffee cherries dominate the lower half, symbolizing peak flavor and readiness for harvest. This is reinforced by a vertical red divider bar.\n\nThe Yellow: A warm, inviting backdrop of a patterned yellow hue suggests the tropical sun and a bright, sunny acidity. Subtly outlined botanical elements add texture without clutter.\n\nThe Green: Distinctive green coffee leaves frame the cherry clusters, representing the natural, organic origin and fresh growth.\n\n\n\nPurpose:\nThe primary purpose of the design is to establish the coffee's exclusive and artisanal nature. The very small net weight of only 50g instantly signals a rare micro-lot or a special sampler pack. The specific, complex tasting notes are not merely described but presented as essential components, guiding the consumer through the curated flavor profile. The design transforms the label from a simple identification marker into a narrative of quality, care, and origin, elevating the coffee from a commodity to an exclusive experience.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2025 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/k12bvi1ml-2025 Coffee Design - Unleashed.jpg","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/f3aa1855-a437-47b0-a208-0873c585c1f2"},{"id":"774v2huqp","name":"2025 Coffee Design - Velvet.jpg","url":"asset://774v2huqp","type":"image","year":"2025","description":"Design Elements:\n\nThe Red: Bold, detailed clusters of ripe coffee cherries dominate the lower half, symbolizing peak flavor and readiness for harvest. This is reinforced by a vertical red divider bar.\n\nThe Yellow: A warm, inviting backdrop of a patterned yellow hue suggests the tropical sun and a bright, sunny acidity. Subtly outlined botanical elements add texture without clutter.\n\nThe Green: Distinctive green coffee leaves frame the cherry clusters, representing the natural, organic origin and fresh growth.\n\n\n\nPurpose:\nThe primary purpose of the design is to establish the coffee's exclusive and artisanal nature. The very small net weight of only 50g instantly signals a rare micro-lot or a special sampler pack. The specific, complex tasting notes are not merely described but presented as essential components, guiding the consumer through the curated flavor profile. The design transforms the label from a simple identification marker into a narrative of quality, care, and origin, elevating the coffee from a commodity to an exclusive experience.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2025 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/774v2huqp-2025 Coffee Design - Velvet.jpg","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/8cdba320-9906-4f55-8af6-4864e3bd03e5"},{"id":"0aozkeng1","name":"2026 Coffee Design - Main.png","url":"asset://0aozkeng1","type":"image","year":"2026","description":"Design\nThe \"Glocal\" Aesthetic: A sophisticated blend of modern corporate structure and traditional Filipino folk art. The clean, matte-white pouches provide a canvas for vibrant, hand-painted illustrations.\n\nVisual Hierarchy: Functional color-coding (Red, Green, Yellow) defines the roast profile, while bold sans-serif typography maintains the professional identity of the Xillium brand.\n\nStorytelling Art: Each label features a central cultural vignette—Dinagyang, Kamayan, and Bayanihan—connecting the product to themes of celebration, community, and cooperation.\n\nPurpose\nCorporate Identity: Humanizes a tech-driven brand by aligning it with heritage and hospitality, making it memorable for clients and partners.\n\nStrategic Gifting: Elevates a standard promotional item into a premium \"Heritage Series\" gift set, designed for high-level networking and brand activation.\n\nExperiential Marketing: Uses sensory cues (specialty tasting notes and roast dates) to bridge the gap between a digital enterprise and a tangible, high-quality physical experience.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2026 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/0aozkeng1-2026 Coffee Design - Main.png","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/c05ad882-47df-4e85-9035-2b0e153ec8f6"},{"id":"a636tw879","name":"2026 Coffee Design - Kickstarter - Xillium LLC.png","url":"asset://a636tw879","type":"image","year":"2026","description":"Design\nThe \"Glocal\" Aesthetic: A sophisticated blend of modern corporate structure and traditional Filipino folk art. The clean, matte-white pouches provide a canvas for vibrant, hand-painted illustrations.\n\nVisual Hierarchy: Functional color-coding (Red, Green, Yellow) defines the roast profile, while bold sans-serif typography maintains the professional identity of the Xillium brand.\n\nStorytelling Art: Each label features a central cultural vignette—Dinagyang, Kamayan, and Bayanihan—connecting the product to themes of celebration, community, and cooperation.\n\nPurpose\nCorporate Identity: Humanizes a tech-driven brand by aligning it with heritage and hospitality, making it memorable for clients and partners.\n\nStrategic Gifting: Elevates a standard promotional item into a premium \"Heritage Series\" gift set, designed for high-level networking and brand activation.\n\nExperiential Marketing: Uses sensory cues (specialty tasting notes and roast dates) to bridge the gap between a digital enterprise and a tangible, high-quality physical experience.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2026 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/a636tw879-2026 Coffee Design - Kickstarter - Xillium LLC.png","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/bc4a17dd-d79b-46d5-b0f3-7d183f5b2ca5"},{"id":"a0z18s7h5","name":"2026 Coffee Design - Black Magic - Xillium LLC.png","url":"asset://a0z18s7h5","type":"image","year":"2026","description":"Design\nThe \"Glocal\" Aesthetic: A sophisticated blend of modern corporate s