.\n\nPurpose\nCorporate Identity: Humanizes a tech-driven brand by aligning it with heritage and hospitality, making it memorable for clients and partners.\n\nStrategic Gifting: Elevates a standard promotional item into a premium \"Heritage Series\" gift set, designed for high-level networking and brand activation.\n\nExperiential Marketing: Uses sensory cues (specialty tasting notes and roast dates) to bridge the gap between a digital enterprise and a tangible, high-quality physical experience.","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"2026 Coffee Design","repoPath":"assets/ee9lp38yy-2026 Coffee Design - Velvet - Xillium LLC.png","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/c03c2e5f-0be7-49cc-80e0-4d8a7a54814c"},{"id":"88lvna0af","name":"Business Cards - Gemini_Generated_Image_st4muqst4muqst4m.png","url":"asset://88lvna0af","type":"image","year":"2025-2026","description":"","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"Business Cards","repoPath":"assets/88lvna0af-Business Cards - Gemini_Generated_Image_st4muqst4muqst4m.png","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/037404ac-b931-4825-af50-b1352b000c5f"},{"id":"06x3kuhpk","name":"Business Cards - Gemini_Generated_Image_u2rx2wu2rx2wu2rx.png","url":"asset://06x3kuhpk","type":"image","year":"2025-2026","description":"","isTemporary":false,"category":"Small Prints","projectName":"Business Cards","repoPath":"assets/06x3kuhpk-Business Cards - Gemini_Generated_Image_u2rx2wu2rx2wu2rx.png","dataUrl":"blob:https://ais-dev-7mtnyci3lbcvs54ocpn3hq-644473134194.asia-east1.run.app/036cfe89-c8cb-460b-89aa-a0ee6cf2c73a"},{"id":"3ik7k4q35","name":"Lanyards 2026 - Gemini_Generated_Image_w8oonnw8oonnw8oo.png","url":"asset://3ik7k4q35","type":"image","year":"2026","description":"displays a coordinated set of three distinct Xillium lanyards, each meticulously designed for a specific operational role. From the classic 